Simple type swap in sample Program.cs files. Change:
  Servers = new Dictionary<string, AsyncApiServer>
  {
      ["production"] = new AsyncApiServer { Host = "...", Protocol = "..." }
  }
To:
  Servers = new Dictionary<string, V3ServerDefinition>
  {
      ["production"] = new V3ServerDefinition { Host = "...", Protocol = "..." }
  }

Add using Neuroglia.AsyncApi.v3; to both files.
Remove using for the old Model namespace.
